#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:1
msgid "模拟实盘交易——CLI 功能清单"
msgstr "模擬實盤交易——CLI 功能清單"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:3
msgid ""
"本文从命令与能力清单角度说明 CLI 中的模拟实盘功能。   如需按步骤操作，请阅读 `tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-"
"broker-walkthrough.md`。"
msgstr ""
"本文從命令與能力清單角度說明 CLI 中的模擬實盤功能。   如需按步驟操作，請閱讀 `tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-"
"broker-walkthrough.md`。"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:6
msgid "0. 文档边界"
msgstr "0. 文檔邊界"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:8
msgid "本页是命令能力索引，不是逐步教程"
msgstr "本頁是命令能力索引，不是逐步教程"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:9
msgid "重点回答“有什么命令、看什么反馈、跳到哪里排查”"
msgstr "重點回答“有什麼命令、看什麼反饋、跳到哪裏排查”"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:11
msgid "1. 命令能力分组"
msgstr "1. 命令能力分組"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:13
msgid "**运行控制**：启动、暂停、恢复、结束"
msgstr "**運行控制**：啓動、暫停、恢復、結束"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:14
msgid "**交易操作**：买入、卖出、撤单"
msgstr "**交易操作**：買入、賣出、撤單"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:15
msgid "**状态查询**：订单、成交、持仓、账户"
msgstr "**狀態查詢**：訂單、成交、持倉、賬戶"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:16
msgid "**诊断与日志**：系统消息、错误提示、任务状态"
msgstr "**診斷與日誌**：系統消息、錯誤提示、任務狀態"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:18
msgid "2. 核心反馈语义"
msgstr "2. 核心反饋語義"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:20
msgid "拒单时可看到英文摘要（含 `rule_id` / `reason`）"
msgstr "拒單時可看到英文摘要（含 `rule_id` / `reason`）"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:21
msgid "分批成交状态更容易在查询结果中识别"
msgstr "分批成交狀態更容易在查詢結果中識別"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:22
msgid "收盘后处理行为通过统一 Broker API 协调"
msgstr "收盤後處理行爲通過統一 Broker API 協調"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:24
msgid "2.1 手工下单的订单类型语义（buy/sell）"
msgstr "2.1 手工下單的訂單類型語義（buy/sell）"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:26
msgid "`buy/sell ... -p 正数`：按**限价单**提交（`order_type='limit'`）"
msgstr "`buy/sell ... -p 正數`：按**限價單**提交（`order_type='limit'`）"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:27
msgid ""
"`buy/sell ...`（不带 `-p`）或 `-p 0`：按**市价单**提交（`order_type='market'`），CLI "
"会在下单前使用最新实时价补齐价格字段"
msgstr ""
"`buy/sell ...`（不帶 `-p`）或 `-p 0`：按**市價單**提交（`order_type='market'`），CLI "
"會在下單前使用最新實時價補齊價格字段"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:29
msgid "在 `SimulatorBroker` 中，撮合判定的关键差异如下："
msgstr "在 `SimulatorBroker` 中，撮合判定的關鍵差異如下："

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "订单类型"
msgstr "訂單類型"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "主要成交条件（简化）"
msgstr "主要成交條件（簡化）"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "`limit` 限价单"
msgstr "`limit` 限價單"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "卖单：实时价 `>=` 挂卖价（含偏差）；买单：实时价 `<=` 挂买价（含偏差）"
msgstr "賣單：實時價 `>=` 掛賣價（含偏差）；買單：實時價 `<=` 掛買價（含偏差）"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "`market` 市价单"
msgstr "`market` 市價單"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "实时涨跌幅位于非涨跌停区间时优先按市价撮合；若接近涨跌停，成交概率显著下降"
msgstr "實時漲跌幅位於非漲跌停區間時優先按市價撮合；若接近漲跌停，成交概率顯著下降"

